## Tools

- enca  # Tool to Detect encoding of text files content and convert them if required.
- convmv  # Tool to converts filenames from one encoding to another

## usage

enca -L zh_CN 中文文件名  # detect encoding of text files
enca -L zh_CN -x utf8 filename  # convert filename to utf8

convmv --list  # list all supported econding
convmv -f utf8 -t gb2312 --notest 中文文件名  # convert filename from utf8 to gb2312
